name: FIGHT CLUB
description:
This artwork digitally hand drawn by myself.
illustrating two robots fighting on boxing arena, while Each robot is controlled by a player from game arena (pumpkin's head).

fight is a competition. in achieving a goal we have to compete and fight with other competitors. Winning or losing is part of the process. the most important thing is that we continue to fight in a fair and respectful way.


NOTE : This edition also particularly created to appreciate some collectors who constantly support and trust my work. most of editions are happily given to those people.
